               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <subc>I,1</subc>; hujus stirpis exemplum equidem nusquam legi; Ludolfus statuit: „<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> tussivit </t:quote></cit>, ex eo quod aliquid in asperam arteriam de cibo vel potu illapsum est“, sine <lbl expand="auctore, auctoritate">auct.</lbl> Prima vis est in <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> asperitate </t:quote></cit> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> : </t:quote></cit> <foreign xml:lang="ar">حَزِيزٌ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> locus salebrosus </t:quote></cit> (<lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐዝሐዝ፡</foreign>); <foreign xml:lang="ar">حَزَازٌ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> furfures capitis </t:quote></cit> et <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> dolor in corde </t:quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">حُزَّازٌ</foreign> et alia nomina (<lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> supra <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐዘነ፡</foreign>), <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚܰܙܳܙܺܝܬܳܐ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> lichen, impetigo </t:quote></cit>; praeterea <lbl expand="conferas">cfr.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="ar">حُزْنَةٌ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">حُزُونَةٌ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">حَزِمٌ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">خَشٌّ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">خَشِبٌ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="ar">خَشُنَ</foreign>; nec non <foreign xml:lang="ar">جَشِرَ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> durus et asper fuit; laboravit tussi, asperitate pectoris </t:quote></cit>. </sense>
               
            <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"><cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ḥazaza</t:quote></cit> <sense n="G"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐዘዘ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ḥazaza</t:quote></cit> <subc>I,1</subc> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ያሐዝዝ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይሕዝዝ፡</foreign> «<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">tousser</t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">être étouffé par la toux</t:quote></cit>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">tussivit eo quod in asperam arteriam de cibo vel potu aliquid illapsum est</t:quote></cit> (<bibl><ptr target="bm:Ludolf1699Lexicon"/></bibl>)» ― <foreign xml:lang="am">አነዘዘ፡</foreign> Ms. <ref type="BM" target="BNFabb217">BNFabb217</ref>, fol. 28r. <lb/>
